HEADWORD: Lancashire boiler
<hw>Lan"ca*shire boil"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A steam
boiler having two flues which contain the furnaces and extend through
the boiler from end to end.</def>⟦br⟧
